Act as a visionary advertiser launching a groundbreaking energy drink for young adults aged 18–30.
Create a campaign that not only promotes the product but inspires a lifestyle.
Define the target audience’s aspirations, craft powerful slogans that resonate with
their identity, and select media channels that capture their attention in bold, 
innovative ways. Design additional activities—such as viral challenges, immersive experiences,
or community events—that transform the drink into a cultural movement. 
Respond with a campaign that feels fresh, exciting, and unforgettable.
